have all the funds you need.

00:14.371 --> 00:15.640
(Gasps)

00:15.642 --> 00:17.811
Its bite is almost
never noticed.

00:17.813 --> 00:21.552
So no evidence implicating
Lorenzo's lover.

00:21.554 --> 00:23.321
May I model for you again?

00:23.323 --> 00:25.893
Go peddle your wares
with Botticelli. He's an easy mark.

00:25.895 --> 00:28.532
Interrogate the victim
mentioned here, Captain.

00:28.534 --> 00:31.705
Once he confirms the charges,
make your arrest.

00:31.707 --> 00:34.276
It has come to the attention
of the Officers of the Night,

00:34.278 --> 00:36.647
